<!-- ===== PROGRAMS ===== -->
<section id="programs">
  <div class="section-label reveal" data-lang-en>Program</div>
  <div class="section-label reveal" data-lang-de>Programm</div>
  <h2 class="section-title reveal" data-lang-en>Our programs.<br /><span class="gradient-text">Hands-on learning.</span></h2>
  <h2 class="section-title reveal" data-lang-de>Unsere Programme.<br /><span class="gradient-text">Lernen durch Machen.</span></h2>
  <p class="section-desc reveal" data-lang-en>Summer camps, workshops, and courses for ages 6&ndash;14. Small groups, bilingual, real engineering.</p>
  <p class="section-desc reveal" data-lang-de>Feriencamps, Workshops und Kurse f&uuml;r 6&ndash;14 Jahre. Kleine Gruppen, zweisprachig, echtes Engineering.</p>
  <p class="section-desc reveal" style="font-size: 13px; color: var(--text-muted); margin-top: -8px;" data-lang-en>Ages are guidelines &mdash; we place each student based on their experience, not just their age.</p>
  <p class="section-desc reveal" style="font-size: 13px; color: var(--text-muted); margin-top: -8px;" data-lang-de>Altersangaben sind Richtwerte &mdash; wir stufen jedes Kind nach Erfahrung ein, nicht nur nach Alter.</p>

  <div class="programs-grid">
    <!-- MAKE MARS GREEN — SUMMER CAMP -->
    <div class="program-card reveal" style="--card-accent: var(--accent-amber); --card-accent-bg: rgba(239,159,39,0.08); --card-accent-border: rgba(239,159,39,0.2);">
      <div class="card-icon"></div>
      <div class="card-age" data-lang-en>Ages 6&ndash;8 &middot; 9&ndash;11 &middot; 12&ndash;14</div>
      <div class="card-age" data-lang-de>Alter 6&ndash;8 &middot; 9&ndash;11 &middot; 12&ndash;14</div>
      <h3 class="card-title" data-lang-en>Make Mars Green</h3>
      <h3 class="card-title" data-lang-de>Make Mars Green</h3>
      <p class="card-desc" data-lang-en>Plant life on Mars &mdash; by remote control. Over 5 days, kids plan and build a system to remotely plant on Mars using real engineering and science. They design, code, and pilot their own Mars device. Hands-on, with real components &mdash; kids keep what they build.</p>
      <p class="card-desc" data-lang-de>Pflanzen auf dem Mars setzen &mdash; per Fernsteuerung. &Uuml;ber 5 Tage planen und bauen Kinder ein System, um aus der Ferne eine Pflanze auf dem Mars zu setzen. Sie konstruieren, programmieren und steuern ihr eigenes Mars-Ger&auml;t. Hands-on, mit echten Bauteilen &mdash; Kinder behalten, was sie bauen.</p>
      <div style="margin-top: 16px; padding-top: 16px; border-top: 1px solid var(--border-subtle);">
        <div class="card-tags">
          <span class="card-tag" data-lang-en>5-day camp</span><span class="card-tag" data-lang-de>5-Tage-Camp</span>
          <span class="card-tag" data-lang-en>3 hours / day</span><span class="card-tag" data-lang-de>3 Stunden / Tag</span>
          <span class="card-tag" data-lang-en>Late July / early Aug 2026</span><span class="card-tag" data-lang-de>Ende Juli / Anfang Aug 2026</span>
          <span class="card-tag" data-lang-en>Max 6 per class</span><span class="card-tag" data-lang-de>Max 6 pro Klasse</span>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div style="margin-top: 16px; padding-top: 16px; border-top: 1px solid var(--border-subtle);">
        <div class="card-tags">
          <span class="card-tag" data-lang-en>English or German</span><span class="card-tag" data-lang-de>Englisch oder Deutsch</span>
          <span class="card-tag" data-lang-en>HK Island &mdash; venue revealed soon</span><span class="card-tag" data-lang-de>HK Island &mdash; Ort folgt</span>
          <span class="card-tag" data-lang-en>No experience needed</span><span class="card-tag" data-lang-de>Keine Vorkenntnisse n&ouml;tig</span>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div style="margin-top: 16px; font-size: 12px; color: var(--text-muted);" data-lang-en>Taught by Daniel Kurth &middot; B.Sc.RWTH Aachen</div>
      <div style="margin-top: 16px; font-size: 12px; color: var(--text-muted);" data-lang-de>Unterrichtet von Daniel Kurth &middot; B.Sc.RWTH Aachen</div>
      <div style="margin-top: 12px; font-size: 12px; color: var(--accent-amber);"><span data-lang-en>&#x2713; All materials included &middot; &#x2713; Kids keep what they build</span><span data-lang-de>&#x2713; Alle Materialien inklusive &middot; &#x2713; Kinder behalten, was sie bauen</span></div>
    </div>

    <!-- THINK. LEARN. PRESENT. -->
    <div class="program-card reveal" style="--card-accent: var(--accent-magenta); --card-accent-bg: rgba(216,90,48,0.08); --card-accent-border: rgba(216,90,48,0.2);">
