      <div class="card-age" data-lang-en>Ages 14+ &middot; Online only</div>
      <div class="card-age" data-lang-de>Ab 14 &middot; Nur online</div>
      <h3 class="card-title">Think. Learn. Present.</h3>
      <p class="card-desc" data-lang-en>Master the science of learning and the art of presenting. Evidence-based memory techniques meet confident public speaking &mdash; skills that last a lifetime.</p>
      <p class="card-desc" data-lang-de>Meistere die Wissenschaft des Lernens und die Kunst des Pr&auml;sentierens. Evidenzbasierte Ged&auml;chtnistechniken treffen auf selbstbewusstes Auftreten &mdash; F&auml;higkeiten f&uuml;rs Leben.</p>
      <div style="margin-top: 16px; padding-top: 16px; border-top: 1px solid var(--border-subtle);"><div style="font-size: 12px; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 1.5px; color: var(--accent-magenta); font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 12px;" data-lang-en>How to Memorize</div><div style="font-size: 12px; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 1.5px; color: var(--accent-magenta); font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 12px;" data-lang-de>Wie man lernt</div><div class="card-tags"><span class="card-tag">Spaced Repetition</span><span class="card-tag">Retrieval Practice</span><span class="card-tag">Interleaving</span></div></div>
      <div style="margin-top: 16px; padding-top: 16px; border-top: 1px solid var(--border-subtle);"><div style="font-size: 12px; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 1.5px; color: var(--accent-magenta); font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 12px;" data-lang-en>The Art of Presentation</div><div style="font-size: 12px; text-transform: uppercase; letter-spacing: 1.5px; color: var(--accent-magenta); font-weight: 600; margin-bottom: 12px;" data-lang-de>Die Kunst der Pr&auml;sentation</div><div class="card-tags"><span class="card-tag">Story Structure</span><span class="card-tag">Slide Design</span><span class="card-tag">Stage Presence</span><span class="card-tag">Q&amp;A Mastery</span></div></div>
      <div style="margin-top: 16px; font-size: 12px; color: var(--text-muted);"><span data-lang-en>Taught by Ananya Singh &middot; M.Sc.RWTH &middot; PhD Candidate</span><span data-lang-de>Unterrichtet von Ananya Singh &middot; M.Sc.RWTH &middot; PhD Candidate</span></div>
